1
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:40,990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:43,979
[Episode 9]

3
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:48,039
I wanted to know what Purong Hotel

4
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:49,479
had become.

5
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:51,890
So what are your thoughts after seeing it?

6
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:53,680
Purong is a big tree

7
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,280
that looks glorious on the outside.

8
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:55,950
In reality,

9
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,750
it has been hollowed out by termites.

10
00:01:57,750 --> 00:01:58,259
Okay.

11
00:01:58,350 --> 00:01:59,350
Second question.

12
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:02,480
What are you exactly doing back this time?

13
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,960
An incognito investigation, right?

14
00:02:09,470 --> 00:02:10,789
I'm not some big shot.

15
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,710
Tell me.

16
00:02:11,710 --> 00:02:14,310
Did you come back to Purong to take over?

17
00:02:15,580 --> 00:02:16,350
Yes.

18
00:02:18,290 --> 00:02:19,890
Chairman Wei asked you back?

19
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,560
Yes.

20
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,280
From the first time I saw you,

21
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:26,690
I knew it.

22
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,540
I knew I couldn't hide it from you.

23
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:32,230
Let me give you a piece of advice.

24
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,490
Leave immediately.

25
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,060
This ship of Purong

26
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:36,800
is going to sink soon.

27
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,030
To be honest,

28
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,060
what you saw today

29
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:43,630
is only the tip of the iceberg in Purong.

30
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:45,590
Do you know how much liquor

31
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:47,840
is wasted in
the Executive Lounge every day?

32
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:50,150
Do you know how many
carts of linen in the Laundry Room

33
00:02:50,150 --> 00:02:52,030
are sent away every day,

34
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:54,120
and how many people take kickbacks?

35
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:56,079
Do you know how long the equipment

36
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,470
in the Engineering Department
hasn't been updated,

37
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:59,310
and whose pockets
the project funds went into?

38
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:01,520
I have investigated
all the problems you mentioned.

39
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,720
Take a look at my investigation report.

40
00:03:06,020 --> 00:03:09,920
[Research Report on Operation and
Management Problems of Purong Hotel]

41
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,520
Rui.

42
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,000
I have 2 reasons
for returning to Purong.

43
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:10,950
[Front Office: Marketing Alienation
and Lack of Service Focus]

44
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:11,740
First,

45
00:03:11,770 --> 00:03:13,890
I've reached the top abroad.

46
00:03:14,170 --> 00:03:15,370
No matter how perfect

47
00:03:15,870 --> 00:03:18,000
I make a hotel,

48
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:19,470
in the end,

49
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:21,030
it still belongs to those

50
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:22,470
blonde-haired, blue-eyed managers.

51
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:23,420
[Executive Lounge: Beverage Waste
and Uncontrolled Costs]

52
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:24,280
But Purong can give me

53
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,870
a place to realize my ambitions.

54
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:26,430
Second,

55
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,690
Purong Hotel is the start of my career,

56
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:32,150
and Chairman Wei is my first mentor.

57
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:34,590
Purong Hotel is now facing

58
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:35,870
a crucial moment.

59
00:03:36,470 --> 00:03:37,630
I really can't bear

60
00:03:37,630 --> 00:03:38,829
and I'm not willing to

61
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:40,240
see Purong Hotel

62
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:42,370
taken away just like that.

63
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:46,680
You are right.

64
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:49,520
But you have to be clear.

65
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,960
Today's Purong Hotel

66
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:53,079
is no longer the famous hotel in Shanghai

67
00:03:53,079 --> 00:03:56,190
under Wei Wanjun in the past.

68
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,910
It's rotten to the core.

69
00:03:57,910 --> 00:03:59,570
What's the use of coming back?

70
00:04:00,590 --> 00:04:01,520
I plan to

71
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:03,890
reorganize Purong Hotel.

72
00:04:05,870 --> 00:04:06,870
Rui, you know

73
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:09,880
what the purpose
of Purong Hotel has always been.

74
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,530
Making guests feel at home.

75
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:13,830
Making guests feel at home.

76
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,480
From the jasmine fragrance in the corridor

77
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,720
to the service specifications
of every detail,

78
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,430
everything should be focused

79
00:04:20,430 --> 00:04:21,959
on the guests' experience.

80
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:23,070
But now?

81
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,510
The current managers
don't care about this at all.

82
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:27,560
They only care about

83
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,920
how to reach into the guests' wallets.

84
00:04:29,940 --> 00:04:32,400
That's why the reputation
is getting worse.

85
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,960
Do you think I don't know?

86
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:37,159
Rui.

87
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:39,350
I'd like to

88
00:04:39,630 --> 00:04:40,460
invite you

89
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,270
to cooperate with me.

90
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,159
Really.

91
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,560
Let's work together

92
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,680
to bring back
the traditions of Purong Hotel

93
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:51,040
and completely reform it
from the inside out.

94
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,300
This is the only way to save Purong Hotel.

95
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,100
I know.

96
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:55,310
I know it's hard.

97
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,720
But it's up to us.

98
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,430
Rui, what conditions do you want?

99
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:58,950
Just tell me,

100
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:00,210
and I'll meet them all.

101
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,120
Wait.

102
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,830
Ji Feng, are you high?

103
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:06,070
I really need you

104
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:07,060
to help me.

105
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,190
Ji Feng.

106
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:11,480
I'm resigning next month

107
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,300
to go to Yiting Siji

108
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:14,520
and work in finance.

109
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,720
The soup dumplings you ordered.

110
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,310
Enjoy.

111
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:24,110
I have no choice.

112
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,220
The situation forces my hand.

113
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:27,560
Within a year,

114
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,360
Purong Hotel changing hands to Kuanli

115
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,120
is almost a foregone conclusion.

116
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:33,190
For a pseudo-middle-class like me,

117
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,000
whether I'm ousted

118
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:35,950
or make it to the top,

119
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:37,680
I have to leave sooner or later.

120
00:05:37,870 --> 00:05:38,600
For the past 10 years,

121
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,630
I've drifted through life

122
00:05:39,630 --> 00:05:41,159
and accomplished nothing.

123
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:43,120
I am not qualified to guide you.

124
00:05:43,270 --> 00:05:45,070
But I want to remind you of one thing.

125
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,270
Things run deep and rough

126
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:47,190
in Purong.

127
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:48,750
In the future,

128
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,180
take care of yourself.

129
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:00,330
Miss,

130
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:02,240
can I add you on WeChat?

131
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:03,510
Sorry, sir.

132
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:04,630
We are not allowed

133
00:06:04,630 --> 00:06:06,560
to add guests on WeChat privately.

134
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:12,750
Sorry to keep you waiting, Mr. Ray.

135
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:14,870
I am an attendant from the HSKP Department
on the executive floor.

136
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:16,510
Is there anything I can help you with?

137
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:17,310
Why is it you?

138
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:19,310
I'm looking for Xu Miyu.

139
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:20,560
Whatever you need,

140
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,560
you can tell me just the same.

141
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,960
What do I have to tell you?

142
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,120
I already said it.

143
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,740
I'm looking for Xu Miyu.

144
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:27,910
Why isn't she serving me?

145
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,620
I'm sorry, sir.

146
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:41,150
Where is your forewoman?

147
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,400
Miyu.

148
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:43,430
Xu Miyu.

149
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:45,400
Ms. Zhang, what is it?

150
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,560
My guest requested room service from you.

151
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,560
Why didn't you go?

152
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,510
Because of your negligence,

153
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:50,310
my guest is feeling very unwell now.

154
00:06:50,310 --> 00:06:51,240
Do you know that?

155
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:57,330
I have to serve many guests every day.

156
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:59,070
I couldn't handle everything at once.

157
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:00,310
I sent a more suitable colleague

158
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,870
who could get there faster.

159
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:04,130
Do I have to report everything to you?

160
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,870
What kind of working attitude is this?

161
00:07:05,870 --> 00:07:06,600
Director Lu,

162
00:07:06,620 --> 00:07:07,800
please don't be angry.

163
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,910
Miyu, stop talking.

164
00:07:08,910 --> 00:07:09,950
Besides, your guest

165
00:07:09,950 --> 00:07:11,210
has been harassing me.

166
00:07:11,930 --> 00:07:13,480
I believe even if the hotel

167
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,260
follows the customer-first principle,

168
00:07:15,260 --> 00:07:16,420
when this happens,

169
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,600
even a regular attendant

170
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,860
has the right to say no.

171
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,830
I already used a very tactful way

172
00:07:21,830 --> 00:07:23,300
to save the guest's face.

173
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,530
I don't think I did anything wrong.

174
00:07:26,390 --> 00:07:27,160
Xu Miyu.

175
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:29,130
Are you suffering from paranoia?

176
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:31,560
My guest would harass you?

177
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,300
What evidence do you have?

178
00:07:40,050 --> 00:07:41,640
You have nothing to say, right?

179
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:42,870
Look in the mirror.

180
00:07:43,110 --> 00:07:44,960
You don't have to use such dirty tricks

181
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:47,110
to flatter yourself, do you?

182
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:50,240
You call this flattering myself?

183
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,240
Is this how you usually

184
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,950
flatter yourself, Director Lu?

185
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:55,159
Your values are so advanced

186
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:57,480
that they're completely out of reach.

187
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,390
Say it again.

188
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,720
Miyu, stop it.

189
00:08:00,740 --> 00:08:02,250
Director Lu, how about this?

190
00:08:02,250 --> 00:08:03,950
I'll ask her to apologize to Mr. Ray

191
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:04,800
to make up for it.

192
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,720
Ms. Zhang,

193
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:09,050
why are you keeping an employee like this?

194
00:08:10,020 --> 00:08:10,600
Director Lu.

195
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,480
Calm down.

196
00:08:13,540 --> 00:08:14,420
You heard her.

197
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,050
Go apologize right now!

198
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:17,600
Well.

199
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:19,500
Why are you still standing here?

200
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:22,160
Aren't you afraid of getting a bad review?

201
00:08:26,780 --> 00:08:27,380
Okay.

202
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,780
I'll go apologize.

203
00:08:43,690 --> 00:08:44,290
Yin Xiang,

204
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,850
can you do me a favor?

205
00:09:00,150 --> 00:09:00,960
Room service.

206
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,480
You're finally here.

207
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:05,960
Come in.

208
00:09:10,990 --> 00:09:11,670
Sorry.

209
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,720
Our hotel has a rule that

210
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,080
during room service,

211
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,540
the door must remain open.

212
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,480
Why didn't you reply to my messages today?

213
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,860
I wanted to buy you dinner,

214
00:09:21,860 --> 00:09:23,120
but you didn't show up.

215
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:24,150
I ordered a bottle of wine.

216
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:25,280
Have a drink with me.

217
00:09:26,530 --> 00:09:27,150
I'm sorry.

218
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:28,490
I can't drink with you.

219
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:29,030
Why?

220
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:31,720
You are the guest,

221
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,920
and I am an attendant.

222
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,720
My job is to

223
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:36,480
provide you with service and help.

224
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:38,030
You might have misunderstood.

225
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:39,480
If there is nothing else,

226
00:09:40,970 --> 00:09:41,900
I will leave now.

227
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,550
Wait.

228
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:45,170
Then help me clear the food.

229
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:02,890
Miyu,

230
00:10:03,370 --> 00:10:04,100
listen to me.

231
00:10:04,940 --> 00:10:07,390
You are different from
the other attendants here.

232
00:10:07,390 --> 00:10:08,460
The moment I first saw you,

233
00:10:08,460 --> 00:10:09,520
I fell for you.

234
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:10,480
Can I hug you?

235
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,740
Don't come any closer.

236
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:18,400
I know good reviews
are very important to you.

237
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:19,530
I will give you a good review.

238
00:10:19,530 --> 00:10:20,590
As many as you want.

239
00:10:24,990 --> 00:10:26,230
I am already recording.

240
00:10:26,230 --> 00:10:27,120
What you just said has already

241
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,360
constituted sexual harassment.

242
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,620
If you don't want me to call the police,

243
00:10:29,620 --> 00:10:30,790
let me out right now!

244
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,240
Sexual harassment?

245
00:10:34,370 --> 00:10:36,140
When did I ever sexually harass you?

246
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:37,670
I haven't even touched you.

247
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,720
You gave me your WeChat ID yourself.

248
00:10:39,940 --> 00:10:42,340
And now you say
I'm sexually harassing you?

249
00:10:44,620 --> 00:10:45,340
Or is it that

250
00:10:46,250 --> 00:10:47,320
you actually hope

251
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:49,080
I really do something?

252
00:10:53,890 --> 00:10:55,070
The Engineering Department
received a maintenance report

253
00:10:55,070 --> 00:10:56,530
for the drain in your room.

254
00:10:58,680 --> 00:10:59,590
Yin Xiang!

255
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:03,150
I didn't report a repair.

256
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:04,280
Leave quickly.

257
00:11:06,330 --> 00:11:07,090
Miyu.

258
00:11:08,230 --> 00:11:08,800
Wait.

259
00:11:09,370 --> 00:11:10,610
The guest just said

260
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:11,320
to let us leave.

261
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,260
What are you doing?

262
00:11:12,260 --> 00:11:13,160
Let's go.

263
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,380
Wait, wait, wait.

264
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:15,570
Didn't you hear?

265
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,260
Something's going to happen.

266
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,360
The guest is inside now.

267
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,080
We don't know the situation.

268
00:11:22,450 --> 00:11:23,650
Forcing the door open

269
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:24,750
will result in punishment

270
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:25,760
and complaints.

271
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:28,290
Don't screw yourself over
and drag us into it.

272
00:11:28,290 --> 00:11:29,090
Open the door!

273
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,530
I'll take responsibility.

274
00:11:31,830 --> 00:11:32,290
Open it.

275
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,060
What are you doing?

276
00:11:42,110 --> 00:11:43,030
Who let you in?

277
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:45,840
I'm sorry, I...

278
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:48,510
I got the wrong room.

279
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:49,750
I called for a repair

280
00:11:50,310 --> 00:11:51,970
and didn't bring my room card.

281
00:12:10,710 --> 00:12:12,640
Sorry, my room should be next door.

282
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:22,580
[Purong Hotel Accommodation
and Conference Contract]

283
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:22,840
Mr. Qian,

284
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,840
if HSKP Department acts like this,

285
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,720
I wouldn't dare
let guests stay here anymore.

286
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,200
I worked so hard to get this order,

287
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:27,960
and it's ruined just like that.

288
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,490
What's the meaning of this?

289
00:12:35,850 --> 00:12:36,630
Don't worry.

290
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:40,020
I'll settle accounts with
the HSKP Department.

291
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:42,120
How do you do things?

292
00:12:42,170 --> 00:12:44,570
How am I supposed to
show my face after this?

293
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:46,240
How am I supposed to hold my head up

294
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:48,240
in front of the sales team next time?

295
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:50,080
Mr. Feng, I'm wronged.

296
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:52,320
It was that Xu Miyu who acted on her own

297
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,550
and made things worse.

298
00:12:53,550 --> 00:12:55,720
I had no time for crisis public relations.

299
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:57,720
Why is it Xu Miyu again?

300
00:12:57,900 --> 00:13:00,970
Didn't I tell you to fire her last time?

301
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,460
I haven't had the time yet.

302
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,720
You hurry up and get rid of her to

303
00:13:06,750 --> 00:13:08,230
make an example of her.

304
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,860
I dare not, Mr. Feng.

305
00:13:09,890 --> 00:13:11,770
She has the guest's leverage.

306
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:13,390
If we fire her now,

307
00:13:13,420 --> 00:13:14,680
it might backfire.

308
00:13:14,780 --> 00:13:15,910
Wait a couple of days

309
00:13:15,910 --> 00:13:17,910
until I find the right opportunity.

310
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:23,860
Mr. Feng, someone is outside to see you.

311
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:26,210
Okay, okay. Go and handle it quickly.

312
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:30,200
He said he is a friend of Mr. Nie Yucheng,

313
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,000
named Ji Feng.

314
00:13:32,670 --> 00:13:33,270
Ji Feng?

315
00:13:37,590 --> 00:13:38,790
Hurry, invite him in.

316
00:13:41,570 --> 00:13:42,370
Wait a minute.

317
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:05,180
Please invite Mr. Ji in.

318
00:14:16,430 --> 00:14:17,100
Miyu,

319
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:18,620
come with me.

320
00:14:24,050 --> 00:14:27,860
[Xu Miyu, 18F,
Morning Shift, Bad Review]

321
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,680
The sales department suffered losses

322
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:32,720
and blamed the HSKP Department.

323
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:34,050
I have no choice either.

324
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,200
Ms. Zhang.

325
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:38,610
I was mentally prepared
for this bad review.

326
00:14:38,910 --> 00:14:39,780
But

327
00:14:40,020 --> 00:14:41,260
I am also a victim.

328
00:14:42,340 --> 00:14:44,560
I shouldn't bear
all the responsibility alone.

329
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:46,620
You should also reflect on yourself.

330
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,630
Why didn't the guest harass others

331
00:14:48,630 --> 00:14:49,870
but harassed you?

332
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:52,310
Did you give the guest the wrong signal

333
00:14:52,310 --> 00:14:54,040
and cause a misunderstanding?

334
00:14:58,770 --> 00:14:59,700
Hello, Mr. Feng.

335
00:14:59,790 --> 00:15:00,960
About your bad review decision,

336
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,680
I am updating Xu Miyu.

337
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:06,910
What?

338
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:15,960
Miyu,

339
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:18,630
don't let me embarrass myself here.

340
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:20,150
You clearly have Black Card Ji

341
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:21,870
as such a strong backer,

342
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:23,650
and you didn't even tell me.

343
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:26,270
You made me look like a fool.

344
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:46,110
What are you doing here?

345
00:15:46,660 --> 00:15:47,890
Hello, Mr. Ji.

346
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:48,960
You came just in time.

347
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:50,390
I have some rotten fruit
in my living room.

348
00:15:50,390 --> 00:15:52,450
Please come in and help me clean it up.

349
00:15:53,140 --> 00:15:53,650
Okay.

350
00:16:21,370 --> 00:16:22,370
How are you doing?

351
00:16:25,270 --> 00:16:26,150
I'm fine.

352
00:16:26,330 --> 00:16:28,760
Thank you for your help this time.

353
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:33,830
I bent the rules for you

354
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:35,450
out of my inner principles.

355
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:40,320
A dignified five-star hotel

356
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:41,760
having to cater

357
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:43,630
to a harasser

358
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,240
is indeed unacceptable.

359
00:16:46,730 --> 00:16:47,390
But that doesn't mean

360
00:16:47,390 --> 00:16:49,580
you're completely
blameless in this matter.

361
00:16:49,580 --> 00:16:50,760
Do you also think

362
00:16:51,110 --> 00:16:53,310
I must've done something to deserve it?

363
00:16:53,560 --> 00:16:54,890
I didn't think that way.

364
00:16:55,250 --> 00:16:56,180
Most of the time,

365
00:16:56,890 --> 00:16:59,790
the relationship between
staff and guests is not equal.

366
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:00,480
This means

367
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:01,320
you must have a stronger

368
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:03,520
sense of self-protection and methods.

369
00:17:03,770 --> 00:17:04,589
The hotel rules state that

370
00:17:04,589 --> 00:17:07,400
staff and guests cannot
contact each other privately.

371
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:09,400
This rule is not only a restriction,

372
00:17:09,869 --> 00:17:11,530
but also a protection for you.

373
00:17:12,290 --> 00:17:13,690
Your people-pleasing mentality

374
00:17:13,690 --> 00:17:14,400
leads you

375
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:16,790
to step outside
the protection of the rules,

376
00:17:16,790 --> 00:17:17,839
step by step,

377
00:17:18,140 --> 00:17:20,740
giving them opportunities
to push their luck.

378
00:17:20,790 --> 00:17:22,119
After that, whether you

379
00:17:23,069 --> 00:17:24,800
have a righteous reason or not,

380
00:17:25,170 --> 00:17:27,170
no matter how cleverly you respond,

381
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:29,280
you will be the one to suffer.

382
00:17:33,730 --> 00:17:35,150
Live and learn.

383
00:17:35,630 --> 00:17:36,630
Next time,

384
00:17:38,040 --> 00:17:40,040
I won't make the same mistake again.

385
00:17:41,550 --> 00:17:43,510
You are quite adaptable.

386
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:03,870
Here.

387
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,790
Thanks, I'm not thirsty.

388
00:18:07,790 --> 00:18:09,050
Apply an ice compress.

389
00:18:17,780 --> 00:18:19,360
At least you had the sense

390
00:18:19,470 --> 00:18:21,060
to call in a colleague with
the Engineering Department crew

391
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:21,950
to help you out.

392
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,240
In the future,

393
00:18:24,470 --> 00:18:26,200
if you encounter
this kind of situation again,

394
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:28,000
you can also come to me directly.

395
00:18:30,370 --> 00:18:31,100
Are you okay?

396
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:44,010
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

397
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,590
Miyu.

398
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:49,350
Miyu.

399
00:18:49,430 --> 00:18:50,270
Come here.

400
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:51,120
Sit.

401
00:18:51,350 --> 00:18:52,370
I want to ask you a question.

402
00:18:52,370 --> 00:18:53,420
Sit.

403
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:55,010
I'm asking you,

404
00:18:55,010 --> 00:18:56,960
how did you get so close to Black Card Ji?

405
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:58,550
Yeah, teach us

406
00:18:58,550 --> 00:19:00,580
your tricks too.

407
00:19:00,750 --> 00:19:01,870
Miyu,

408
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:05,160
is that guy the type who is cold
on the outside but warm on the inside?

409
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:08,030
Cold as ice on the surface,

410
00:19:08,050 --> 00:19:09,510
but once he commits to you,

411
00:19:09,550 --> 00:19:11,810
he will go through fire and water for you.

412
00:19:13,630 --> 00:19:15,330
You read too many wish-fulfillment novels.

413
00:19:15,330 --> 00:19:16,860
What's wrong with wish-fulfillment novels?

414
00:19:16,860 --> 00:19:18,930
A strong, beautiful,
and tragic female lead

415
00:19:18,930 --> 00:19:21,040
protected by a domineering CEO,

416
00:19:21,060 --> 00:19:24,560
outsmarting a bunch
of crazy and obsessive monsters.

417
00:19:24,630 --> 00:19:27,360
Dare you say your dopamine didn't spike?

418
00:19:27,380 --> 00:19:28,900
Didn't it spike?

419
00:19:29,700 --> 00:19:31,200
What are you all talking about?

420
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:32,470
I don't understand at all.

421
00:19:32,470 --> 00:19:34,510
This is not the script of my life.

422
00:19:34,540 --> 00:19:36,510
It's okay, Miyu.

423
00:19:36,790 --> 00:19:38,830
We're already shipping it.

424
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:41,720
With a mysterious VIP
giving you a boost, your life

425
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:43,290
is about to take off.

426
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:48,390
Shipped it.

427
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:49,920
So sweet.

428
00:19:53,120 --> 00:19:53,880
Hello, Neil.

429
00:19:54,230 --> 00:19:55,070
Any updates?

430
00:19:55,620 --> 00:19:56,950
Happy birthday, Mr. Ji.

431
00:19:57,310 --> 00:19:58,000
Thank you.

432
00:19:58,350 --> 00:19:59,030
Mr. Ji,

433
00:19:59,030 --> 00:20:01,020
did you sign the contract with Landi?

434
00:20:01,020 --> 00:20:01,880
Yeah, it was me.

435
00:20:01,950 --> 00:20:03,720
I've signed it for a couple of weeks.

436
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:04,650
Anything wrong?

437
00:20:09,660 --> 00:20:11,330
Andy is on this contract.

438
00:20:11,670 --> 00:20:14,890
And it seems that Landi is suing us

439
00:20:15,110 --> 00:20:18,410
for some loopholes in
the imported horses protection clause.

440
00:20:18,410 --> 00:20:19,450
Happy birthday.

441
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:20,530
Okay, thank you.

442
00:20:20,530 --> 00:20:21,020
Please.

443
00:20:21,540 --> 00:20:22,870
Tell me more about that.

444
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:23,740
Take your time.

445
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,810
Tell Andy to get in touch with me.

446
00:20:28,110 --> 00:20:29,150
I'll wait for him.

447
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:32,430
Happy birthday.

448
00:20:32,430 --> 00:20:33,650
Hello, Mr. Ji.

449
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:34,900
Today is your birthday.

450
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:36,980
On behalf of all the service staff
on the executive floor,

451
00:20:36,980 --> 00:20:38,510
I wish you a happy birthday.

452
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,110
Thank you.

453
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:42,740
Mr. Ji,

454
00:20:42,930 --> 00:20:43,750
our executive floor

455
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:46,000
provides special
birthday services for guests.

456
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:48,000
Private dining rooms for up to 20 guests,

457
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:50,120
as well as party spaces
for up to 80 guests,

458
00:20:48,220 --> 00:20:48,810
[Dear Mr. Ji, in the year ahead,]

459
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:49,070
[may your life be as
beautiful as poetry, filled with joy,]

460
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:49,310
[sunshine,]

461
00:20:49,340 --> 00:20:49,980
[and surprises. Happy Birthday.]

462
00:20:50,140 --> 00:20:52,270
do not require advance reservations.

463
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:53,790
Got it.

464
00:20:54,270 --> 00:20:55,440
Tell the others

465
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:57,640
not to say happy birthday to me anymore.

466
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:00,110
Mr. Ji,

467
00:21:00,110 --> 00:21:01,480
what would you like to eat?

468
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:03,160
The usual. Thanks.

469
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:03,720
Okay.

470
00:21:06,030 --> 00:21:06,640
Okay.

471
00:21:07,340 --> 00:21:08,640
If you need anything,

472
00:21:08,750 --> 00:21:10,030
please feel free to contact me.

473
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:10,640
Okay.

474
00:21:10,670 --> 00:21:11,470
Thanks.

475
00:21:11,650 --> 00:21:12,720
[Andy]

476
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:19,750
Is this Andy?

477
00:21:21,230 --> 00:21:21,860
Great.

478
00:21:22,130 --> 00:21:24,230
I have something to discuss with you.

479
00:21:24,750 --> 00:21:25,830
The kitchen

480
00:21:25,830 --> 00:21:27,200
is already preparing
the birthday fruit platter.

481
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:28,330
Should we cancel it?

482
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:31,120
Why cancel?

483
00:21:31,300 --> 00:21:33,820
Free items still need
to be put on the tab.

484
00:21:34,280 --> 00:21:35,520
Then who is going to deliver it?

485
00:21:35,520 --> 00:21:36,450
I'll arrange it.

486
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:38,120
You guys,

487
00:21:38,320 --> 00:21:40,250
just need to keep your mouths shut.

488
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:47,150
Miyu.

489
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:49,340
Make sure the service for room 1812

490
00:21:49,340 --> 00:21:50,500
is spot on today.

491
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:51,620
Later,

492
00:21:51,830 --> 00:21:53,870
I'll send you the birthday schedule.

493
00:21:53,870 --> 00:21:55,900
Set the mood right.

494
00:22:00,090 --> 00:22:01,050
Room service.

495
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:04,440
Hello, room service.

496
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:06,830
Mr. Ji.

497
00:22:06,830 --> 00:22:07,360
Wish...

498
00:22:07,380 --> 00:22:08,970
Just give it a quick sweep.

499
00:22:10,370 --> 00:22:11,170
Andy.

500
00:22:12,450 --> 00:22:13,850
Happy birthday.

501
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:20,490
Since this incident
occured in the isolated facility,

502
00:22:20,620 --> 00:22:22,470
that was not under our control.

503
00:22:24,590 --> 00:22:26,850
We shouldn't be held responsible for it.

504
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,760
We bought the horses,

505
00:22:32,780 --> 00:22:35,330
but they don't officially
belong to us yet.

506
00:22:37,240 --> 00:22:40,470
The seller shall be
responsible for any risks.

507
00:22:40,940 --> 00:22:41,920
This was clearly

508
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,160
stated in the contract.

509
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,160
The seller didn't have third-party

510
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:46,020
disease coverage for the horses.

511
00:22:46,580 --> 00:22:47,680
They then infected

512
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:48,960
all 100 high-value horses

513
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:50,590
in quarantine.

514
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:52,750
We lost over 10 million dollars.

515
00:22:53,650 --> 00:22:55,920
Now they want to shift
the blame to our hotel.

516
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:57,270
Find the contract immediately.

517
00:22:57,270 --> 00:22:59,530
They can't dodge their responsibility.

518
00:23:00,120 --> 00:23:02,050
I'm looking for the contract here.

519
00:23:02,900 --> 00:23:03,630
But, Ji Feng,

520
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:05,160
you signed the contract

521
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:06,110
before you left.

522
00:23:07,170 --> 00:23:07,740
Hold on.

523
00:23:15,860 --> 00:23:17,510
The group just sent a formal notice.

524
00:23:17,510 --> 00:23:19,400
If this contract

525
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:21,330
causes major final losses to the hotel,

526
00:23:21,330 --> 00:23:22,960
the manager who signed the contract

527
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,890
will be blacklisted internationally.

528
00:23:24,890 --> 00:23:25,950
Do you understand?

529
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:28,590
This means that in
European and American hotel systems,

530
00:23:28,590 --> 00:23:32,240
you will never be hired.

531
00:23:41,330 --> 00:23:42,110
Ji Feng.

532
00:23:42,250 --> 00:23:42,790
Excuse me.

533
00:23:42,790 --> 00:23:43,700
You can't come in.

534
00:23:43,700 --> 00:23:44,440
Who are you?

535
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,290
Mind your own business.

536
00:23:45,290 --> 00:23:45,990
Ji Feng.

537
00:23:47,340 --> 00:23:48,620
You can't come in.

538
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:50,200
Do you know who I am?

539
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:55,880
Happy birthday.

540
00:23:57,880 --> 00:23:58,420
Mr. Duan,

541
00:23:58,450 --> 00:23:59,180
we...

542
00:24:02,790 --> 00:24:04,030
Ta-da!

543
00:24:04,030 --> 00:24:04,720
-Happy birthday!
-What is this?

544
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:05,850
Happy birthday!

545
00:24:05,870 --> 00:24:06,750
Happy birthday!

546
00:24:06,750 --> 00:24:07,350
Thank you.

547
00:24:07,550 --> 00:24:08,270
-Happy birthday.
-Thank you.

548
00:24:08,270 --> 00:24:09,200
Happy birthday!

549
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:10,300
-Just a little noise.
-Happy birthday!

550
00:24:10,300 --> 00:24:12,480
-To help you shake the dust off the ceiling.
-Happy birthday!

551
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:13,440
Are you trying to shake the ceiling

552
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:14,900
or blow my head off?

553
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:18,730
Wait a minute.

554
00:24:18,730 --> 00:24:20,080
Help me entertain the guests.

555
00:24:20,080 --> 00:24:21,030
Mr. Duan, excuse me.

556
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:21,750
I need to take a call.

557
00:24:21,750 --> 00:24:22,550
Excuse me for a moment.

558
00:24:22,550 --> 00:24:23,250
Go.

559
00:24:26,010 --> 00:24:28,200
Let's go party!

560
00:24:30,480 --> 00:24:31,030
Come on.

561
00:24:31,030 --> 00:24:31,640
Attendant.

562
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:33,240
Come here and build a champagne tower.

563
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:35,100
If you break it, you have to drink.

564
00:24:35,490 --> 00:24:36,720
Close the curtains.

565
00:24:36,720 --> 00:24:37,240
It's broad daylight.

566
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:38,270
There's no atmosphere for drinking.

567
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:39,400
I'll close the curtains.

568
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:40,530
Queue up some songs.

569
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:42,440
Queue up the songs.

570
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:51,880
[Meeting Details]

571
00:24:42,460 --> 00:24:43,200
Hi, Andy.

572
00:24:44,170 --> 00:24:45,670
I can't find the contract.

573
00:24:47,440 --> 00:24:48,300
Are these okay?

574
00:24:48,750 --> 00:24:51,210
Go find the backup copy
of your contract now.

575
00:24:51,480 --> 00:24:51,960
Hurry.

576
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:54,410
I can't find the backup either.

577
00:24:54,590 --> 00:24:58,530
[Meeting Details]

578
00:24:54,630 --> 00:24:55,240
I suspect

579
00:24:55,240 --> 00:24:56,640
Landi bribed someone in our hotel

580
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:58,680
to destroy the contract and its backup.

581
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:00,340
They're clearly out to get us.

582
00:25:02,240 --> 00:25:03,240
Speaking of that,

583
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:05,430
I signed a memorandum with them.

584
00:25:05,830 --> 00:25:08,200
All the necessary information
and signatures are there.

585
00:25:08,140 --> 00:25:15,100
[Meeting Details]

586
00:25:08,750 --> 00:25:09,680
I'll look for it right now.

587
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,350
You don't still have it, do you?

588
00:25:11,350 --> 00:25:13,000
It's just my way of doing things.

589
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:15,330
I have to.
There are so many traps to avoid.

590
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:30,070
[Horse Purchase and Sales Contract]

591
00:25:44,030 --> 00:25:46,830
Happy birthday to you.

592
00:25:46,940 --> 00:25:49,930
Happy birthday to you.

593
00:25:50,010 --> 00:25:53,350
Happy birthday to you.

594
00:25:53,350 --> 00:25:56,960
Happy birthday to you.

595
00:25:57,090 --> 00:25:58,400
Happy birthday.

596
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:05,350
Are you okay?

597
00:26:05,350 --> 00:26:06,750
Who pushed me?

598
00:26:06,750 --> 00:26:08,210
My buddy's cake is ruined.

599
00:26:26,630 --> 00:26:28,290
Is this thing important?

600
00:26:28,750 --> 00:26:29,320
Get out.

601
00:26:30,930 --> 00:26:31,740
Get out!

602
00:26:32,850 --> 00:26:33,950
Let's go.

603
00:26:37,560 --> 00:26:38,190
Mr. Ji.

604
00:26:38,220 --> 00:26:39,320
I told you to get out!

605
00:26:39,320 --> 00:26:42,980
Do you people on the executive floor
not understand human speech?

606
00:27:04,320 --> 00:27:06,030
I said I wasn't celebrating my birthday.

607
00:27:06,030 --> 00:27:08,110
Yet you brought a bunch of people
into my room to make a mess.

608
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:09,730
I didn't bring these people in.

609
00:27:09,730 --> 00:27:11,130
Then who brought them in?

610
00:27:11,130 --> 00:27:12,230
Did they break down the door?

611
00:27:12,230 --> 00:27:13,630
You opened the door

612
00:27:13,650 --> 00:27:14,740
and let them in.

613
00:27:15,110 --> 00:27:16,960
And you even made
some flower arrangement for me.

614
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:18,400
Did you think by showing off like that

615
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:20,060
I would give you a good review?

616
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:21,110
It's not like that.

617
00:27:21,110 --> 00:27:22,000
Let me ask you,

618
00:27:22,220 --> 00:27:24,480
how does your
HSKP Department serve guests?

619
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:25,440
Is it based on the guests' needs,

620
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:26,840
or your own preferences?

621
00:27:27,130 --> 00:27:28,140
What a mess.

622
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:30,550
Do you believe I'll complain about you?

623
00:27:30,820 --> 00:27:32,460
I already told you,

624
00:27:32,650 --> 00:27:34,150
I didn't bring the guests in,

625
00:27:34,150 --> 00:27:36,090
and this mess wasn't
caused by our executive floor.

626
00:27:36,090 --> 00:27:37,380
On what grounds are you
complaining about me?

627
00:27:37,380 --> 00:27:39,300
My birthday is my privacy.

628
00:27:39,380 --> 00:27:40,160
Whether I celebrate it

629
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:41,710
and who I invite to celebrate with me,

630
00:27:41,710 --> 00:27:42,800
is for me to decide.

631
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:44,680
You're violating my privacy right now.

632
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,440
That alone

633
00:27:45,470 --> 00:27:46,550
is enough for me to file
a complaint against you.

634
00:27:46,550 --> 00:27:48,360
You say I invaded your privacy, right?

635
00:27:48,360 --> 00:27:49,660
Then as a consumer,

636
00:27:49,740 --> 00:27:51,440
you didn't respect
my right to know either.

637
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:52,830
How did I not respect your right to know?

638
00:27:52,830 --> 00:27:53,680
Mr. Ji,

639
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:55,290
do I need to remind you?

640
00:27:55,360 --> 00:27:56,740
Just a month ago,

641
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:58,270
in the hotel where you
were the general manager,

642
00:27:58,270 --> 00:27:59,680
you kept telling me

643
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,880
that the underwear on my bed

644
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:02,550
was left by the previous guest.

645
00:28:02,550 --> 00:28:03,830
You said, "Mrs. Nie,

646
00:28:03,830 --> 00:28:05,160
please rest assured.

647
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:06,440
I have looked into it.

648
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:07,400
This underwear

649
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:09,100
has absolutely nothing
to do with your husband."

650
00:28:09,100 --> 00:28:10,500
Nie Yucheng is innocent.

651
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:12,500
I didn't say your husband was innocent.

652
00:28:12,500 --> 00:28:13,070
Right.

653
00:28:13,230 --> 00:28:14,910
You didn't use the word "innocent."

654
00:28:14,910 --> 00:28:16,680
But you spun the lie so perfectly

655
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:18,550
that you made me believe he was innocent.

656
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:19,640
You made me believe

657
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:21,200
my marriage was rock solid.

658
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:22,350
I didn't lie.

659
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:23,160
I...

660
00:28:23,550 --> 00:28:24,270
I just...

661
00:28:26,490 --> 00:28:28,090
I just didn't tell the whole truth.

662
00:28:28,090 --> 00:28:29,710
Not telling the whole truth?

663
00:28:29,790 --> 00:28:31,070
You were taking things out of context,

664
00:28:31,070 --> 00:28:31,880
confusing right and wrong,

665
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:32,640
misleading me with selective details,

666
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:34,840
and making sweeping generalizations.

667
00:28:35,250 --> 00:28:37,480
Did your conscience
allow you to say that?

668
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:39,110
Is that how you treat your
guests and the trust

669
00:28:39,110 --> 00:28:41,310
they place in you—with such hypocrisy?

670
00:28:41,320 --> 00:28:42,880
You keep saying

671
00:28:43,380 --> 00:28:44,480
you serve your guests

672
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:45,540
and think for them.

673
00:28:46,110 --> 00:28:48,440
You speak in such high-sounding words,

674
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:50,480
but what you do is so hypocritical

675
00:28:50,500 --> 00:28:51,710
and perfunctory.

676
00:28:52,100 --> 00:28:53,140
Mr. Ji,

677
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,840
are you really thinking for your guests?

678
00:28:54,840 --> 00:28:57,000
I think you're probably
just using sweet words

679
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:59,400
to build a persona
as a gold-medal manager.

680
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,270
Your own marriage...

681
00:29:01,390 --> 00:29:02,550
Your own marriage failed,

682
00:29:02,550 --> 00:29:03,550
and you don't examine yourself,

683
00:29:03,550 --> 00:29:04,750
but blame me instead.

684
00:29:04,860 --> 00:29:06,200
Don't you think you're ridiculous?

685
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,780
Yes, I am ridiculous.

686
00:29:07,800 --> 00:29:09,460
I'm the laughingstock
of the whole world now.

687
00:29:09,460 --> 00:29:10,200
But don't you think

688
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,720
you have a part in this?

689
00:29:11,800 --> 00:29:12,750
If it weren't for you

690
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:14,310
helping my ex-husband lie to me,

691
00:29:14,310 --> 00:29:15,240
would my life now

692
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:16,820
be reduced to this?

693
00:29:17,270 --> 00:29:18,750
You say you think for your guests.

694
00:29:18,750 --> 00:29:19,920
You say all you think about

695
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:20,830
are the guests' interests.

696
00:29:20,830 --> 00:29:21,550
I think all you think about

697
00:29:21,550 --> 00:29:22,790
are your own interests.

698
00:29:22,790 --> 00:29:23,960
Your KPI.

699
00:29:23,960 --> 00:29:24,240
I...

700
00:29:24,260 --> 00:29:25,240
If Nie Yucheng couldn't

701
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:26,350
bring you a few clients,

702
00:29:26,350 --> 00:29:28,630
would you need to suck
up to him so desperately?

703
00:29:28,630 --> 00:29:29,690
The funny thing is,

704
00:29:29,720 --> 00:29:31,440
I even thought after
I came to Purong Hotel

705
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:32,590
you had been helping me.

706
00:29:32,590 --> 00:29:34,440
Actually, it's because of
your guilty conscience, right?

707
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:36,400
Because you are
my ex-husband's accomplice.

708
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:37,960
No matter how many masks you wear,

709
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:39,880
you're a hypocritical wretch to the bone!

710
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:40,710
If I were you,

711
00:29:40,730 --> 00:29:43,130
I'd look in the mirror
and examine myself carefully.

712
00:29:43,130 --> 00:29:44,740
If it weren't for your own
weakness and incompetence,

713
00:29:44,740 --> 00:29:46,270
coveting wealth and glory,

714
00:29:46,270 --> 00:29:47,850
blindly pleasing your ex-husband,

715
00:29:47,850 --> 00:29:49,810
how could he be so fearless

716
00:29:49,840 --> 00:29:51,850
and act wildly right under your nose?

717
00:29:51,850 --> 00:29:53,130
You're looking for an accomplice, right?

718
00:29:53,130 --> 00:29:54,460
Let me tell you, Xu Miyu,

719
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:57,240
your ex-husband's
biggest accomplice is you!

720
00:30:01,930 --> 00:30:04,870
I want to file a complaint against
an attendant from the HSKP Department.

721
00:30:04,870 --> 00:30:05,700
Executive floor,

722
00:30:05,700 --> 00:30:06,550
Xu Miyu.

723
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:08,170
She was rude to a guest

724
00:30:08,170 --> 00:30:10,230
and had a terrible service attitude.

725
00:30:55,850 --> 00:30:56,850
[Album]

726
00:30:56,890 --> 00:30:57,460
[Photo]

727
00:30:57,740 --> 00:31:01,120
[Horse Purchase and Sales Contract]

728
00:31:07,130 --> 00:31:09,140
[Horse Ownership]

729
00:31:12,780 --> 00:31:14,530
[Send]

730
00:31:14,740 --> 00:31:15,590
[Inbox]

731
00:31:35,730 --> 00:31:36,490
Hi, Andy.

732
00:31:36,700 --> 00:31:37,760
That's great.

733
00:31:38,270 --> 00:31:39,470
We're gonna win it.

734
00:31:40,330 --> 00:31:41,860
I can't believe we made it.

735
00:31:41,970 --> 00:31:43,300
Man, you are a true hero.

736
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:45,520
How I wish I were.

737
00:31:46,170 --> 00:31:48,200
I only ask to be treated like a person.

738
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,130
What did you say?

739
00:31:50,560 --> 00:31:51,920
What I just said is...

740
00:31:54,100 --> 00:31:54,850
Forget it.

741
00:31:55,130 --> 00:31:56,790
I don't know how to express it.

742
00:31:57,320 --> 00:31:57,960
Ji Feng.

743
00:31:58,280 --> 00:31:59,000
Listen.

744
00:31:59,810 --> 00:32:01,870
You should have a drink to celebrate.

745
00:32:02,670 --> 00:32:03,470
Good idea.

746
00:32:03,580 --> 00:32:04,530
Have a good night.

747
00:32:04,530 --> 00:32:05,860
Okay, have a good night.

748
00:32:34,210 --> 00:32:35,830
You say you think for your guests.

749
00:32:35,830 --> 00:32:36,960
You say all you think about

750
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:37,880
is the guests' interests.

751
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:38,550
I think all you think about

752
00:32:38,550 --> 00:32:39,830
are your own interests.

753
00:32:39,830 --> 00:32:41,030
Your KPI!

754
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:42,200
Isn't it just that Nie Yucheng

755
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:44,240
can bring you some client resources?

756
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:46,530
Do you have to try
so hard to suck up to him?

757
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:47,540
I tell you.

758
00:32:47,590 --> 00:32:49,550
You are an accomplice of my ex-husband.

759
00:32:49,550 --> 00:32:51,110
No matter how many masks you wear,

760
00:32:51,110 --> 00:32:53,440
you're a hypocritical wretch to the bone!

761
00:33:04,710 --> 00:33:07,110
[Employee Schedule]

762
00:33:07,110 --> 00:33:14,850
[Xu Miyu, 18F,
Morning Shift, Bad Review]

763
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:25,410
Miyu.

764
00:33:25,470 --> 00:33:28,200
You haven't taken out
the seasoning packets yet.

765
00:33:37,410 --> 00:33:38,210
We got paid.

766
00:33:39,260 --> 00:33:41,050
Full bonus, 5,500.

767
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:42,730
How much did you get, Xiang?

768
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:44,110
Eight thousand?

769
00:33:43,930 --> 00:33:44,590
[Minfu Bank]

770
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:45,590
Nine thousand?

771
00:33:45,150 --> 00:33:46,950
[Transaction Notification:
Transaction Amount 7,350 RMB]

772
00:33:46,160 --> 00:33:46,960
Ten thousand?

773
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:48,130
How much did you get?

774
00:33:48,440 --> 00:33:49,400
Not that much.

775
00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:51,450
You have to treat me anyway.

776
00:33:53,360 --> 00:33:55,820
[Transaction Notification:
Transaction Amount 2,800 RMB]

777
00:34:24,110 --> 00:34:25,310
Hello, Officer Wang.

778
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:26,620
Ms. Xu,

779
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:27,770
I'm calling to inform you

780
00:34:27,770 --> 00:34:29,550
that the suspect
in the rental fraud and theft case

781
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:30,480
has been caught.

782
00:34:30,739 --> 00:34:31,340
Really?

783
00:34:32,550 --> 00:34:34,080
But you should be prepared.

784
00:34:34,150 --> 00:34:36,750
Your financial loss
is likely unrecoverable.

785
00:34:38,190 --> 00:34:39,070
I understand.

786
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:16,630
[Road closed]

787
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:16,030
Xu Miyu.

788
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:22,030
Are you Ms. Xu Miyu?

789
00:35:22,670 --> 00:35:24,270
Who are you?

790
00:35:24,290 --> 00:35:25,690
You don't know who we are?

791
00:35:26,070 --> 00:35:27,670
Then what are you hiding for?

792
00:35:28,710 --> 00:35:30,440
Not answering calls

793
00:35:30,460 --> 00:35:31,580
or messages.

794
00:35:32,190 --> 00:35:32,840
What?

795
00:35:33,000 --> 00:35:34,000
Trying to renege?

796
00:35:36,650 --> 00:35:39,380
No, my bonus got deducted recently.

797
00:35:39,510 --> 00:35:41,330
I really don't have money.

798
00:35:41,380 --> 00:35:43,300
Can you give me 2 more days?

799
00:35:43,420 --> 00:35:45,050
I sympathize with you, Ms. Xu,

800
00:35:45,050 --> 00:35:46,320
but telling me this

801
00:35:46,340 --> 00:35:47,440
is useless.

802
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:48,800
Everyone who can't pay back

803
00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:49,930
says the same thing.

804
00:35:50,040 --> 00:35:51,980
Can you say something new?

805
00:35:52,810 --> 00:35:55,830
Even if you make up a story,
make it a good one.

806
00:35:56,890 --> 00:35:58,340
Don't be nervous, Ms. Xu.

807
00:35:58,650 --> 00:36:00,520
We are just workers too.

808
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:03,690
I hope you can understand.

809
00:36:03,720 --> 00:36:04,990
Just easily

810
00:36:05,070 --> 00:36:06,250
give us the money,

811
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:07,880
so we can all go home and rest early.

812
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:08,780
Right?

813
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:09,400
I...

814
00:36:10,290 --> 00:36:12,760
I really don't have a single cent.

815
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:14,070
Give me 2 more days.

816
00:36:14,070 --> 00:36:16,000
I will definitely find a way, okay?

817
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:18,280
What should we do?

818
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:19,410
She said 2 more days.

819
00:36:21,670 --> 00:36:22,400
How about this?

820
00:36:22,400 --> 00:36:24,530
I'll treat you to some coffee,

821
00:36:24,550 --> 00:36:25,990
and we can talk somewhere else.

822
00:36:25,990 --> 00:36:28,550
Ms. Xu, you have more to say to us?

823
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:30,210
Not really.

824
00:36:35,670 --> 00:36:36,590
How about this?

825
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:38,010
We know a place

826
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:39,870
where it's easy

827
00:36:40,080 --> 00:36:41,550
to make money overnight.

828
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:43,010
How about it?

829
00:36:43,570 --> 00:36:45,260
I know you're not the type

830
00:36:45,290 --> 00:36:47,070
to intentionally default on a debt.

831
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:47,600
Let's go.

832
00:36:48,220 --> 00:36:49,480
Let's go drink coffee.

833
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,360
Let me go.

834
00:36:50,640 --> 00:36:51,840
You're quite strong.

835
00:36:52,440 --> 00:36:53,320
Let me go!

836
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:54,280
These are my colleagues.

837
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,030
I'll scream!

838
00:36:55,050 --> 00:36:55,960
Okay.

839
00:36:56,060 --> 00:36:58,350
- Call your colleagues over then.
- Let me go!

840
00:36:58,350 --> 00:36:59,070
Let her go!

841
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:02,360
I heard everything.

842
00:37:02,750 --> 00:37:04,080
I'll give you the money.

843
00:37:06,260 --> 00:37:07,000
If you said that earlier,

844
00:37:07,000 --> 00:37:08,520
this wouldn't have happened.

845
00:37:08,520 --> 00:37:09,030
Come on.

846
00:37:09,250 --> 00:37:10,530
[Lu Ming; Ming]

847
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:10,800
[Loading]

848
00:37:10,950 --> 00:37:12,330
[Payment to an individual]

849
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:16,880
Excuse me,

850
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:18,700
are you her colleague, sir?

851
00:37:18,730 --> 00:37:19,860
Leave immediately,

852
00:37:19,890 --> 00:37:21,220
or I'll call the police.

853
00:37:22,550 --> 00:37:23,150
Thank you.

854
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:23,930
Let's go.

855
00:37:30,810 --> 00:37:31,660
Are you okay?

856
00:37:33,070 --> 00:37:33,730
I'm fine.

857
00:37:36,430 --> 00:37:37,090
Thank you.

858
00:37:37,850 --> 00:37:38,650
It's nothing.

859
00:37:40,390 --> 00:37:42,520
I will pay you back as soon as possible.

860
00:38:01,680 --> 00:38:02,590
[Your business loan
has been automatically repaid]

861
00:38:02,610 --> 00:38:03,710
[for ¥5,000. Your payment
for this month has been settled]

862
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:10,480
Life is truly ironic.

863
00:38:10,710 --> 00:38:11,800
The ones you love

864
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:13,230
and trust

865
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:16,330
betray and leave you one by one.

866
00:38:17,570 --> 00:38:19,910
The one who repeatedly
saves you from trouble

867
00:38:19,910 --> 00:38:20,710
is always the one

868
00:38:20,710 --> 00:38:22,840
you should cross paths with the least.

869
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:26,840
I'm starting to hate my own
pitifulness and weakness.

870
00:38:34,550 --> 00:38:35,400
Room service.

871
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,800
Hello, room service.

872
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:17,810
Mr. Ji,

873
00:39:17,840 --> 00:39:18,720
you're here.

874
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:47,670
Can you sew?

875
00:39:49,430 --> 00:39:51,030
Otherwise, sew it yourself.

876
00:40:11,060 --> 00:40:11,550
Done.

877
00:40:11,810 --> 00:40:12,410
Thank you.

878
00:40:20,300 --> 00:40:21,000
By the way.

879
00:40:22,190 --> 00:40:23,360
About last night,

880
00:40:23,710 --> 00:40:24,400
thank you.

881
00:40:25,620 --> 00:40:28,390
[IOU]

882
00:40:27,550 --> 00:40:28,280
This is the IOU.

883
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:28,760
No need.

884
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:30,400
It was no trouble.

885
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:32,980
You must accept it.

886
00:40:33,070 --> 00:40:34,330
I don't want to owe you.

887
00:40:55,070 --> 00:40:55,800
Miyu.

888
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:57,360
Sit.

889
00:41:07,370 --> 00:41:08,050
Miyu.

890
00:41:09,190 --> 00:41:10,670
Did you

891
00:41:12,190 --> 00:41:13,360
offend Madam Cailu?

892
00:41:15,110 --> 00:41:15,840
No.

893
00:41:16,510 --> 00:41:17,360
Why do you ask?

894
00:41:19,480 --> 00:41:20,670
A couple of days ago,

895
00:41:21,280 --> 00:41:21,920
I heard her

896
00:41:21,920 --> 00:41:23,860
talking to someone on the phone.

897
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:25,360
She said

898
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:27,040
she wants to fire you.

899
00:41:29,070 --> 00:41:29,840
What?

900
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:31,960
Why?

901
00:41:32,590 --> 00:41:33,590
I don't know,

902
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:35,320
b-but I heard it with my own ears.

903
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:36,450
I'm not lying to you.

904
00:41:37,710 --> 00:41:38,970
That's impossible.

905
00:41:39,550 --> 00:41:40,950
I've never offended her.

906
00:41:43,070 --> 00:41:44,730
When did you hear her say that?

907
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,630
Last...

908
00:41:47,920 --> 00:41:48,920
Last Tuesday.

909
00:41:49,470 --> 00:41:50,560
In the Linen Room.

910
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:53,000
I was outside and heard her talking.

911
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:55,650
She was speaking very anxiously.

912
00:41:55,880 --> 00:41:58,080
It seemed like something had happened.

913
00:42:14,440 --> 00:42:16,030
Last time you asked me
to get 2 bottles of shampoo

914
00:42:16,030 --> 00:42:17,430
from 2 different places,

915
00:42:17,480 --> 00:42:18,610
what was that about?

916
00:42:20,550 --> 00:42:23,070
I can't tell you
too many details right now.

917
00:42:23,590 --> 00:42:25,150
The whole story hasn't

918
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:27,100
been fully investigated yet.

919
00:42:28,690 --> 00:42:29,840
Then give me a sample.

920
00:42:29,840 --> 00:42:30,670
I'll help you look into it.

